^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|well I think Patti had a good inkling to try for slam, but then she chickened out unfortunately. Let's see why a good slam is such a good bet. It makes any time hearts are 2-1 or you guess the hearts. And given my preempt, easy to guess the hearts. First, let us add up Patti's Bergen Points. She has 13 HCP, plus two for length points and one for Aces/tens exceed (three Aces and one Ten) the quacks. |
